Rest DSR Capsule (157441)
Dignosis: ('ACS - Acute coronary syndrome', 'UTI - Urinary tract infection')
Notes: No sugar - no sweet in diet. to take rice & potato in less amount. to avoid fasting and meal skipping. to walk 3-4 km  / day. take sugar or glucose if you feel giddy - tremor - perspiration (hypoglycemia). restrict salted and oily (ghee-butter-oil) food beverages - no papad - no pickles., Do not eat sour food items. avoid excessive sunlight / noice exposure. avoid fasting & meal skipping. avoid sleep deprivation. do not eat cheese / cheese product / chocolate  etc.(dairy products).
